[Student "S"]
{Following SOUTH's Jacoby 2NT, NORTH bids 3\S. This is stronger than 4\S and 
shows a 6-card suit.

SOUTH has already bid the full strength of his hand so he signs off with 4\S which NORTH passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
